    "On the other hand, it needs to be emphasized that major improvement in CNN effectiveness, is primarily the result of the rearrangement of the processing elements and the introduction of new blocks.",
    "The use of network depth was among the most innovative breakthroughs in CNN.",
    "Figure 3.1 gives the timeline of various CNN architectures.",
    "LeNet.One of the inaugural CNNs, LeNet-5, contributed to the evolution of Deep Learning.",
    "In the year 1998 paper, \"Gradient-Based Learning applied to Document Recognition,\" [61] introduced LeNet."
